thread.title: Kent Heberlig
thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Kent Heberlig

author: Kent Heberlig
title: Kent Heberlig
text: This is the second pair of complete prescription glasses I have purchased from Frames Direct. Although my first choice was not available, the large selection made finding something else very easy. And the lenses are great. I will be a repeat customer. Thank you Frames Direct.
